race.description: Gold Coast Magic Millions Rising Stars F&M Plate
race.comment: SOUTHERN HEIRESS (11) returned in good order with a close-up second at Randwick and will have derived a stack of benefit from that hit-out. Gets gun hoop McDonald in the hot seat and can improve enough to take this out. SCRIPTED (8) hasn't done much wrong with two wins and two seconds from four career outings with Mallyon being in the saddle for three of those efforts. Has to be included. MAMUSHKA (6) has only missed a drum once in seven career starts and will be high on confidence following that first-up victory. In the mix. YES LULU (4) will be rock-hard fit for this and must be respected out of the Maher yard. Shapes as a key runner. ALTERMATUM (10) is an honest commodity who doesn't know how to run a bad race. A must for the multiples.
